{"tid":1277184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要做嘅係守住呢一代。","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:50:55.000Z","uid":31058,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea43497453b9628a566e591b29e93d766b379958","tid":1277184,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"一定要企出黎 守住呢一代<br />\n支持中共同建制嘅9成都係廢老<br />\n而換血係必然發生嘅事 <br />\n就算係10年 20年 30年都好<br />\n只要我地守住呢一代 教育下一代<br />\n有發開夢嘅人都知 香港人係高質嘅 <br />\n香港人係值得擁有民主<br />\n就算民主係我地呢一代實現唔到 <br />\n我地都要整靚個場 交俾下一代接力<br />\n呢個係長期抗爭 我地仲有希望！<br />\n呢個月黎經歷過咁多場一齊發嘅夢<br />\n我地要將呢個夢一齊發埋落去<br />\n香港人加油。"},{"pid":"352262c8e5c144fe3dfee496c445eaf479782a2a","tid":1277184,"uid":31058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c567bc6cf76cd94b72131ba24e3f59f23e4eca4","tid":1277184,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"守護公義 守護下一代"},{"pid":"04c3a964d92875a38d4cc6d7107e502fe5ae188f","tid":1277184,"uid":271867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"守既 仲有教育同跨境學童<br />\n依加中學都已經一堆蝗 個個放學都講普通話"},{"pid":"f2e78cd2013a6f5eda2b7f832ae144954b76f28f","tid":1277184,"uid":31058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04c3a964d92875a38d4cc6d7107e502fe5ae188f","tid":1277184,"uid":271867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"守既 仲有教育同跨境學童<br />\n依加中學都已經一堆蝗 個個放學都講普通話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"其實好多00後都有企出黎 大部份嘅學生都係有思想 唔好放棄佢地"},{"pid":"074763a9fa0e2fa3206801d8c0d02989b0168381","tid":1277184,"uid":271867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2e78cd2013a6f5eda2b7f832ae144954b76f28f","tid":1277184,"uid":31058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04c3a964d92875a38d4cc6d7107e502fe5ae188f","tid":1277184,"uid":271867,"like":1,"dislike":